Question: There are more containers of a colorful fluid on the left than on the right.

Reference Answer: True

Original program:

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='How many containers of colorful fluid are in the image?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='How many containers of colorful fluid are in the image?')
ANSWER2=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} > {ANSWER1}')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER2)
```
